    - "hashlib.algorithms_guaranteed.__contains__('sha3_512') == True — sha3_512 is in the guaranteed set. Verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "hashlib.algorithms_guaranteed.__contains__('blake2b') == True — blake2b is in the guaranteed set. Verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "hashlib.algorithms_guaranteed.__contains__('blake2s') == True — blake2s is in the guaranteed set. Verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
